title: Janis Ross
text:
Janis Ross (born 7 June 1962) is an <a href="England">English</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> footballer.
She competed at the <a href="1998%20Women%27s%20Rugby%20World%20Cup">1998 Women's Rugby World Cup</a>,
She played for <a href="Richmond%20F.C.">Richmond FC</a>, and Saracens.
